    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-08-25T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-08-25T12:00:00-05:00" n="190"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d190">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.2131/55: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dawson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-08-25T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >August 25, 1933—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 2:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>76. Legation’s 74, August 19, 8 p.m. Miguel López Pumarejo, New York
                    representative of National Federation of Coffee Growers, is being <pb
                        facs="0314" n="226" xml:id="pg_226"/> appointed additional adviser. Other
                    experts will arrive New York September 5th S.S. <hi rend="italic">Santa
                        Maria.</hi>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
